<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= title %></title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <div class="card">
      <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <span>How do I create a quiz?</span>
          <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>
            To create a quiz, you need to be registered and logged in. Once
            logged in, go to your dashboard and click on the "Create a Quiz"
            button. Follow the instructions to add questions and answers.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <span>Can I edit a quiz after publishing it?</span>
          <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>
            Yes, you can edit your quizzes at any time. Go to your dashboard,
            find the quiz you want to edit, and click on the "Edit" button.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <span>How are quiz scores calculated?</span>
          <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>
            Quiz scores are calculated based on the number of correct answers.
            Each question can have different point values assigned by the quiz
            creator.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-4">
        <a href="/" class="btn">Back to Home</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  </body>
</html>
